Thank you so much @cetaphil.pt and @hivency for sending me over this magnificent product ♥️

Did you know that May is Sensitive Skin Month and that Cetaphil products are suitable for this skin type?

 This cleansing lotion is Cetaphil's most iconic product, it's for daily use, it gently cleanses the skin while providing hydration and comfort to the skin, being indicated for sensitive and delicate skin, it is a product of high tolerance, and protects against the Five Sensitive Skin Signs: Dryness, irritation, roughness, tightness and a weakened skin barrier.
Here are the features of Cretaphil Cleansing Lotion:
 • Protects against the 5 signs of sensitive skin.
• Removes dirt, make-up and other impurities.
• Gently cleanses and moisturizes the skin.
• Helps maintain the skin's natural hydration.
• Can be removed with or without water •
 Non-comedogenic.
• High tolerance, can be used on sensitive and delicate skin.

 This cleansing lotion can be applied to dry skin directly with your hands and massaged in, removing the excess with a cotton ball (as I did in the video), or it can be applied to the skin and then rinsed off with water.

This product can be found in all pharmacies (in Portugal).

- vitamin C: I been trying this one for a week now and I love it, I love the texture and the smell
